OL,3,CMan stepped into path of double-decker
OL,4,Cbus, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest into the death of Samuel
OL,7,FMcAuley has found he died from severe
OL,8,Fhead and chest injuries.
OL,10,FThe 26-year-old was struck by a double-
OL,11,Fdecker bus near City Hall in Belfast
OL,12,Fin January 2023.
OL,14,FOn Thursday, an inquest into his death
OL,15,Fwas both opened and closed by senior
OL,16,Fcoroner Joe McCrisken.
OL,18,FIt heard statements from eyewitnesses
OL,19,Fand also evidence from the PSNI's
OL,20,FCollision Investigation Unit.
