OL,6,FA compilation of CCTV was shown
OL,7,Fcapturing the moments leading up to
OL,8,Fand during the collision.
OL,10,FIn an autopsy report, the forensic
OL,11,Fpatholgist found Mr McAuley suffered
OL,12,Fvery severe injuries, mostly to his
OL,13,Fhead and chest.
OL,15,FShe also stated he had a high alcohol
OL,16,Fconcentration in his blood.
