OL,3,CMan stepped into path of double-decker
OL,4,Cbus, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe coroner found that Mr McAuley, who
OL,7,Fwas with a female friend, attempted to
OL,8,Fcross the road and stepped into the
OL,9,Fpath of the bus when it was not safe
OL,10,Fto do so and it was probable he did
OL,11,Fnot recognise the risks.
OL,13,FMr McCrisken also found that there was
OL,14,Fno fault on the part of the bus driver.
OL,16,FHe indicated that there was an
OL,17,Fimportant safety lesson to be learned
OL,18,F- that pedestrians should use proper
OL,19,Froad crossings when available.
